tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE user_interaction_data (
    user_id STRING PRIMARY KEY,
    interaction_type STRING,
    interaction_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    device_id STRING,
    app_version STRING
);

CREATE TABLE user_data (
    user_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    interaction_type VARCHAR(50),
    interaction_timestamp TIMESTAMP,
    device_id INT,
    AR_app_id INT
);

CREATE TABLE AR_applications (
    AR_app_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    app_name VARCHAR(50),
    developer VARCHAR(50),
    release_date DATE,
    usage_count INT
);

CREATE TABLE user_feedback (
    feedback_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT,
    AR_app_id INT,
    feedback_text TEXT,
    rating INT
);

CREATE TABLE ar_usage_stats (
    stat_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    app_id INT,
    user_id INT,
    interaction_id INT,
    timestamp TIMESTAMP
);
